message: "If you reference this model or its numbers, please cite it as below and include the version — figures change across methodology revisions."
title: "Frontier Inference Margins: an interactive model of frontier-LLM serving costs and unit margins"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Ashita Orbis"
version: v2.1.6
date-released: 2026-07-15
url: "https://margins.ashitaorbis.com"
repository-code: "https://github.com/AshitaOrbis/inference-margins"
license: MIT
abstract: >-
  An open scenario model of what it costs to serve one token of a frontier LLM and the
  modeled unit direct-serving contribution margin that implies, with per-platform anchored
  effective-MFU fits, a typed public-claims registry, published negative results, and a
  full research annex. Estimates, not provider disclosures.
